Package org.frank.entity

Class Entity

java.lang.Object
org.frank.entity.Entity
Direct Known Subclasses:
Axe, Banana, Door, GreenSlime, HealthBar, Hoe, InteractiveTile, Mushroom, Oscael, Player, PlayerCutsceneDummy, Projectile, Shield, SingleBed, StoreClerk, Sword, SwordCopper
public abstract class Entity extends Object
Represents a general entity in the game, including the player, NPCs, and monsters, objects, tools. Handles common attributes and behaviors such as movement, collision, drawing on the screen, and interactions with other entities.
